What you need to know:

There are many girls, women, boys and men experiencing GBV, who urgently need a safe place but can’t find any.Shelters are overstretched with many on the edge of shutting down due to financial constraints.Maisha Girls safe house, MaryFaith Children’s Centre and Woman’s Hope shelter, constitute the 36 shelters in Kenya not enough to accommodate the rising cases of GBV in the country.